title: Beautiful Gems Watch Face
summary: Beautiful gems sparkle and glisten to your delight with this watch face.
description: Make telling the time a pleasure with this beautiful watch face.  This rhinestone studded surface will sparkle as bright as stars as you move your wrist to tell the time.  Move it around and enjoy the eye candy.  The date is shown in your local format.  The time and date appear clearly on this watch face for your smartwatch.  This smartwatch watch face will shine and gives you a cute look on your watch.There are many different colors to choose from.  Pick the one that is right for you or mix it up whenever you please.  Every color stands out with wonderful glitter.This watch face tells the time in 12 hour and 24 hour modes.  It shows the date in an easy to read fashion.To access the settings menu, long-press on the screen and scroll to the watch face.  The settings menu can be opened by tapping on the gear beneath the preview image.When downloaded, search for it in you Android Wear app.  If you do not have Android Wear, you can download it from Google Play.  If the watch face does not appear, check to see if it is already installed on your smart watch.  You can also go to Settings > Resync Apps in Android Wear.
descriptionHTML:
Make telling the time a pleasure with this beautiful watch face. This rhinestone studded surface will sparkle as bright as stars as you move your wrist to tell the time. Move it around and enjoy the eye candy. The date is shown in your local format. The time and date appear clearly on this watch face for your smartwatch. This smartwatch watch face will shine and gives you a cute look on your watch.

There are many different colors to choose from. Pick the one that is right for you or mix it up whenever you please. Every color stands out with wonderful glitter.

This watch face tells the time in 12 hour and 24 hour modes. It shows the date in an easy to read fashion.

To access the settings menu, long-press on the screen and scroll to the watch face. The settings menu can be opened by tapping on the gear beneath the preview image.

When downloaded, search for it in you Android Wear app. If you do not have Android Wear, you can download it from Google Play. If the watch face does not appear, check to see if it is already installed on your smart watch. You can also go to Settings > Resync Apps in Android Wear.
